Channel home-sent
Channel home-arch

IMAPStore itsg-remote
Host itsg.home.pl
Port 993
User kdowolski@itsg.com.pl
PassCmd "pass poczta.home.pl/kdowolski@itsg.com.pl"
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore itsg-local
Path ~/.mail/itsg/
INBOX ~/.mail/itsg/inbox

Channel itsg-inbox
Expunge Both
