Slave :itsg-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"

IMAPStore starfish-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User kdowolski@starfishstorage.com
PassCmd "pass accounts.google.com/kdowolski@starfishstorage.com"
Timeout 0
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

MaildirStore starfish-local
Path ~/.mail/starfish/
Subfolders Verbatim
INBOX ~/.mail/starfish/inbox

